Company Overview of LocalShares Investment Trust - Nashville Area ETF



Snapshot People




Company Overview
LocalShares Investment Trust - Nashville Area ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by LocalShares, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Decker Wealth Management LLC. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies that are headquartered in Nashville. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations with a market capitalization above $100 million. It seeks to replicate the performance of the LocalShares Nashville Index, by investing in stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. LocalShares Investment Trust - Na...
LocalShares Investment Trust - Nashville Area ETF is an exchange traded fund launched and managed by LocalShares, Inc. The fund is co-managed by Decker Wealth Management LLC. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in stocks of companies that are headquartered in Nashville. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in stocks of companies operating across all market capitalizations with a market capitalization above $100 million. It seeks to replicate the performance of the LocalShares Nashville Index, by investing in stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. LocalShares Investment Trust - Nashville Area ETF was formed on July 31, 2013 and is domiciled in the United States.
